    "before": "Because this isn't really a \"month\" in the traditional sense, but rather the entire 1961 summary, I won't be listing issue numbers, but I wanted you to get a flavor for some of the other magazines that shared rack space with the 5 books that are part of this archive.\n\n<b>No joke:&nbsp; </b>This is what the company was publishing on a regular basis at the dawn of Marvel Comics.",
